data.description: **** PRICE IMPROVEMENT****Are you and your family looking for the perfect home, well, here it is. This beautiful brick 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home is sitting on almost 1.5 acres with space for days. Build on or build up around this home. This house is nestled in a quiet neighborhood on a private lot. It also has a large open split floor plan with beautiful hardwood floors throughout the main living area. The master bedroom has tons of space and a sitting area. The spa-like bathroom will take your breath away. There is a side load garage with plenty of storage. The large backyard with an amazing tree line is perfect for kids or entertaining! Please don't let this one pass you by!
